<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.5.5">
<l>kaṟṟiṉam mēyttuk kaṉikkoru kaṉṟiṉai</l>
<l>paṟṟiye ṟinta paramaṉ tirumuṭi</l>
<l>yuṟṟaṉa pēcinī yōṭit tiriyātē</l>
<l>yaṟṟaikkum vantukuḻal vārāyak kākkā</l>
<l rend="indent">yāḻiyāṉ ṟaṉkuḻal vārāyak kākkāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Coming everyday to the divine head of the Supreme lord,</l>
<l rend="indent">who, while grazing the herd of calves,</l>
<l rend="indent">grabbed one calf and threw it for fruit,</l>
<l>without running around, wandering about,</l>
<l>talking about [all] the things that happened,</l>
<l>Caw! Caw!Comb [his] curly hair.</l>
<l>Caw! Caw! Comb the curly hair of the discus lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
